.Dt TOASCII 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm toascii
.Nd convert a byte to 7-bit ASCII
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In ctype.h
.Ft int
.Fn toascii "int c"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn toascii
function strips all but the low 7 bits from a letter,
including parity or other marker bits.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The
.Fn toascii
function always returns a valid ASCII character.
